raw_text = "~ start
## 1pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Nina: Ugh. Of course it had to be this
Player: Nina?
Nina: Don't get excited, this isn't a social call
Nina: Jessica cooked up some dumbass \"task\" for us girls today
Nina: And it was a short straw for me
Player: Doing what exactly?
Nina: ...
Nina: Boys pick what girls wear today 🙄
Nina: So apparently I gotta let you play dress up with me. Kill me now
- Sounds fun to me [#blackheart]
	set Story.black_heart += 1
	Player: Sounds fun to me
	Nina: HAH. Course you'd say that, perv
	Nina: Keep grinning, genius, see where it gets you
- Whatever you want
	Player: Whatever you want
	Nina: Ugh. Spineless. Why am I not surprised
Nina: Let's get this over with before I torch the whole idea
Nina: I laid out two things
Nina: Don't overthink it, it's not like your taste matters
Nina: Just pick your poison and let me be on my way
Nina: img: nina/22
Nina: This is what I was gonna wear
Nina: img: nina/23
Nina: But I guess I could go with this too
Nina: I'd rather set it on fire but, y'know. \"Rules are rules\" apparently 🙄
Nina: So spit it out already
- Leather Jacket
	set Story.flag = \"Nina1A\"
	Player: Leather Jacket
	Nina: Didn't think you were into that kind of thing loser
	Nina: Fine
- Hoodie
	set Story.flag = \"Nina1B\"
	Player: Hoodie 👀
	Nina: Knew you were a simpleton
	Nina: Bet you're staring at my tits huh?
	Nina: Closest you'll ever get, so savor it
Nina: Finally done with this weird convo
Nina: Now buzz off, I've got real things to do
- Cya
	Player: Cya
- 🖕
	Player: 🖕
Nina: 🖕
do social_post(\"nina_dressup\")
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
